name: ROCKSTAR LIFESTYLE BY TRE SMITH (C/o L Connect)
description: During the COVID-19 Pandemic, I took on a commission based project, to design a 420 themed collection, with a Cleveland based clothing company called, L-Connect. During the design process, Nicky & I Always thought to take our vectorized designs, and put them in the NFT space. Through HEN, that is now possible.
